Title: The method of direct expansions of Feynman integrals

Authors: S.A. Larin

Comments: 7 pages, latex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B514 (2001) 366-370

The universal method of expansion of integrals is suggested. It allows inparticular to derive the threshold expansion of Feynman integrals.